Name: One Bullet left
About the game: Start with nothing and try to erase every enemies in the area. To help you along your way is a large selection of gadgets, weapons and triggerable stuff and bullet time management to assassinate your targets in any way you like. Your main weapon is pistol,rifle for now but we are planning to add many other weapons and gadgets.
